last_episode_to_air.name: John Cena
last_episode_to_air.overview: John Cena has signed the deal to finally sit in the Hot Seat on this star-studded episode, featuring Ashton Kutcher and Danny Masterson.

name: Unfiltered with Renee Young
overview: WWE announcer Renee Young interviews WWE Superstars and other pop-culture celebrities, covering just about everything, except what they are famous for.

episodes.name: Seth Rollins
episodes.overview: In the premiere of Unfiltered, Renee Young hangs out with WWE World Heavyweight Champion Seth Rollins for a fun and revealing conversation!

episodes.name: Hot Pursuit
episodes.overview: Host Renee Young chats with Reese Witherspoon and Sofia Vergara, stars of the new movie, Hot Pursuit, as well as director, Anne Fletcher!

episodes.name: Wiz Khalifa
episodes.overview: Renee Young hangs out with Wiz Khalifa for a fun and revealing conversation!

episodes.name: King Barrett
episodes.overview: Renee Young chats with the King of the Ring Bad News Barrett, discussing everything from music, marine biology and everything in between!

episodes.name: Entourage
episodes.overview: Renee Young hangs out with the cast of Entourage to discuss their behind-the-scenes experience of the movie in theaters June 3rd!

episodes.name: Darren Young
episodes.overview: Renee sits down with Darren Young in this unfiltered and revealing conversation.

episodes.name: Magic Mike XXL
episodes.overview: Renee Young sits down with the cast of Magic Mike XXL, including star Channing Tatum, Joe Manganiello, and WWE Hall of Famer Kevin Nash.

episodes.name: Ant-Man
episodes.overview: Renee Young gets her superhero on. Join the Unfiltered host as she hangs out with star Paul Rudd and the cast of Marvel's Ant Man!

episodes.name: Nikki Bella
episodes.overview: Renee Young gets up close and personal with Nikki Bella in this supersized Unfiltered conversation!

episodes.name: Stephen Amell
episodes.overview: With his match against Stardust and King Barrett looming, Renee and Stephen discuss everything from Arrow to TMNT 2 to his love of WWE!

episodes.name: Summer Rae
episodes.overview: Renee and Summer Rae do brunch in Columbus, Ohio and discuss everything from her time in the LFL to working with Marvel to being a WWE Diva!

episodes.name: Randy Orton
episodes.overview: Renee Young exposes a side of Randy Orton that the WWE universe has never seen before in this special, extended Unfiltered interview!

episodes.name: Kevin Owens
episodes.overview: Renee Young and Kevin Owens discuss everything from his anti-Canadian views on beer and sports, to his pets, to his debut against John Cena!

episodes.name: Finn Balor
episodes.overview: Renee sits down with NXT Superstar Finn Balor as they discuss growing up in Ireland, his favorite movies and his surprising love for legos.

episodes.name: Lita
episodes.overview: Renee sits down with former WWE Diva Lita to discuss her new role within WWE, butterflies and a Twitter moment with a famous rap legend

episodes.name: The Miz
episodes.overview: Aweeesome! Renee goes Hollywood with The Miz and discusses everything from his love life and puppies to his passion for acting and karaoke!

episodes.name: Sasha Banks
episodes.overview: In this B.A.D edition of Unfiltered, Renee sits with Sasha Banks and chats about relaxing, K-Pop, and her family ties to Snoop Dogg.

episodes.name: Star Wars: The Force Awakens
episodes.overview: Renee Young chats with JJ Abrams and the cast of Star Wars: The Force Awakens in a WWE exclusive interview about the making of the movie.

episodes.name: Dolph Ziggler
episodes.overview: On this holiday edition of Unfiltered; Renee talks to Dolph Ziggler about stand-up comedy, pranks, and being a dancer for Britney Spears.

episodes.name: Roman Reigns
episodes.overview: Season 2 kicks off as Renee talks childbirth and dancing with Roman Reigns and psycho-analyzes the WWE roster with Dr. Phil.

episodes.name: Charlotte
episodes.overview: Renee lounges with Charlotte to talk about her Irish step-dancing skills and superhero dreams. Summer Rae and R-Truth venture backstage.

episodes.name: Cesaro
episodes.overview: Cesaro joins Renee for a formal interview about his cat Klaus, sewing, and Swiss cheese. Plus, a shocking announcement from the Chairman.

episodes.name: Paige
episodes.overview: A mischief filled episode as Paige and Renee discuss underwear, whiskey, and shrimp. Plus, a chat with WWE Kids and some fun with Maryse.

episodes.name: Dean Ambrose
episodes.overview: Dean Ambrose brings the Asylum to talk Bigfoot, 'woofs', and the happy bowl sandwich. Summer Rae and R-Truth are backstage, at it again.

episodes.name: Chris Jericho
episodes.overview: A reluctant Chris Jericho joins Renee Young to chat about music, celebs, and all things Canadian. Plus, Jon Stewart stops by for some fun.

episodes.name: Becky Lynch
episodes.overview: The Hot Seat features Becky Lynch for Twitter Talk and Gaelic lessons. Plus, Renee goes backstage for some Unfiltered Superstar Thoughts.

episodes.name: Enzo & Big Cass
episodes.overview: Enzo and Big Cass sit down ‘one-on-two’ with Renee to find out how well they truly know each other. Plus, some holiday mischief backstage!

episodes.name: John Cena
episodes.overview: John Cena has signed the deal to finally sit in the Hot Seat on this star-studded episode, featuring Ashton Kutcher and Danny Masterson.
